column2:
'Auth mode'
"No auth isn't supported for managed online endpoint. If you use the upgrade scripts, it"
'will convert it to key auth. For key auth, the original keys will e used. Token-ased auth'
'is also supported.'
'TLS'
"For ACI service secured with HTTPS, you don't need to provide your own certificates"
'anymore, all the managed online endpoints are protected y TLS.'
